---
title: HelloHero: Herby Bacon & Leek Pasta with Garden Salad & Parmesan Cheese
description: Perfectly al dente pasta mixed through a creamy sauce is too good to be true. There’s plenty of veggies hidden in amongst the penne to keep things fresh and green. For a bit of fun, throw in some diced bacon and leek and you’ve cooked another pasta winner dinner.

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with penne due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your
recipe card!*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R1027_W21_NZ_Main_high-2e2aeff2.jpg
